high_descs: Move to the table to the right of the fridge.
Pick up a loaf of bread from the table.
move to the fridge to the left of you.
Open the fridge and place the bread inside and chill for a moment before retrieving the bread and closing the door.
Move to the counter to the left of you and to the right of the sink.
Place the bread on the counter.
anns.task_desc: Put a chilled loaf of bread on the counter to the right of the sink.

high_descs: Turn around and then go to the table on your left.
Pick up a loaf of bread from the table.
Turn left and go to the fridge.
Chill the bread and then take it back out of the fridge.
Turn left and walk to the counter.
Put the bread on the counter to the right of the sink.
anns.task_desc: Put chilled bread on the counter by the sink.

high_descs: Turn around, head straight, then turn left and head to the table with the bread.
Pick up the front bread on the table.
Bring the bread to the fridge on the left.
Chill the bread in the fridge.
Bring the chilled bread to the counter left of the fridge, right of the sink.
Put the chilled bread on the counter right of the tomato.
anns.task_desc: Put chilled bread on the counter.

high_descs: Turn around, hang a left at the brown chair and walk to the white table.
Pick up the loaf of bread to the left of the knife with a yellow handle on the table.
Turn left and walk to the fridge on your right.
Put the bread inside the fridge on the top shelf in the middle, let it chill for seven seconds, remove the bread from inside and close the door.
Turn left and walk to the counter top to the right of the sink.
Place the bread behind the egg and to the right of the tomato on the counter.
anns.task_desc: Place a chilled loaf of bread on a counter.

high_descs: Turn around and go to the left to the white table.
Pick up the piece of bread that is in the front.
Take the bread, turn to the left and then the right to find the fridge.
Open fridge and put the bread inside then shut the door. Open the door, and take the bread out and shut the door.
Take the bread and turn left to the counter.
Put the bread on the counter to the right of the egg.
anns.task_desc: Chill a loaf of bread and move it to the counter.
